u.s. feb consum credit rose 1.77 billion dlr u.s. consum instal credit rose a season adjust 1.77 billion dlr in februari after a revis rise of 789 mln dlr in januari , the feder reserv board said . the annual rate of growth in februari wa 3.7 pct , up from 1.6 pct in januari . previous the fed said consum credit rose 536 mln dlr in januari . among the credit categori , auto credit rose in februari by 717 mln dlr after increas 416 mln dlr in januari , the fed said . revolv credit in februari rose 1.04 billion dlr after fall by 23 mln dlr in januari . mobil home credit wa down by 59 mln dlr in februari after rise 141 mln dlr in januari . the categori refer to as `` other , '' cover bank and credit union loan , increas by 74 mln dlr in februari after rise by 255 mln dlr in januari , the fed said . befor season adjust , consum credit outstand total 576.05 billion dlr at the end of februari , compar with 530.41 billion dlr at the end of februari , 1986 .